descriptionByLocale.en:
Pemsa is a leading employment agency in Switzerland, specialized in construction, civil engineering, electricity, building technology and industry. With a deep knowledge of the local market and a broad and qualified network, Pemsa actively supports companies and professionals by offering tailor-made recruitment solutions and high quality consulting services. Our mission is to enhance human capital by promoting jobs of excellence and motivated candidates, to build together a solid and sustainable professional future. ## Mission:
• Installation and installation of sanitary facilities with precision and compliance with Swiss regulations in force;
• Construction of heating systems, ensuring energy efficiency and reliability of plant solutions;
• Management and optimization of the use of materials, ensuring a sustainable approach and devoid of waste during all stages of work;
• Active collaboration with the technical team for the execution of projects, maintaining high quality standards;
• Interventions at localized yards up to 20 km from the candidate's residence, ensuring punctuality and efficiency in transfers. ## Profile:
• Minimum experience of 5 years in Switzerland in the field of laying sanitary and heating systems, demonstrating technical mastery and knowledge of local regulations;
• Residence within a maximum radius of 20 km from the workplace, to ensure presence and operational flexibility;
• Italian mother tongue, necessary to communicate effectively with the team and customers;
• Driving license category B, indispensable for travel with company vehicles;
• Excellent knowledge of the materials used in sanitary and heating systems, with the ability to properly manage supply and use;
• Proven capacity for laying sanitary and heating systems, in compliance with safety and quality procedures.
• Useful requirements: Reading and interpretation of technical design to ensure accuracy in the performance of installations;
• Preferable experience in in insole works, for better integration in specialized yards;
• Bonus: Possession of the AFC (Federal Capacity Certificate) professional qualification in the field, as a certificate of qualified training. ## Ton interlocuteur/trice : At Pemsa, our dedicated interlocutor will be an expert recruitment consultant in the technical and construction sector, able to accompany you along the entire selection and insertion path. We offer customized support, based on in-depth knowledge of the specific needs of our customers and the enhancement of the skills of candidates. We work to ensure transparency, professionalism and concrete opportunities for professional development. Nous ne répondrons qu’aux candidatures dont le profil correspond au descriptif demandé.

